headline: Keysight Showcases Solutions Driving Radio Frequency and Millimeter-Wave Innovation at European Microwave Week 2025
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., September 08, 2025--Keysight will demonstrate radio frequency (RF) and millimeter-wave (mmWave) innovation across industries, IoT networks, 5G, and 6G applications.

headline: A Look at Keysight Technologies's Valuation Following Latest Test Solution and Smart Bench Product Launches
summary: If you have been keeping an eye on Keysight Technologies (KEYS), the recent stream of product launches might have caught your attention. The company has just rolled out an enhanced physical layer compliance test solution for HDMI, tailored to tackle the demanding needs of ultra-high definition video and high-speed connectivity. Alongside this, Keysight introduced its Smart Bench Essentials Plus lineup, targeting engineers who need an extra dose of accuracy and reliability to navigate...
